{"type":"message","id":"7d137573","parentId":"475eb375","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:34:13.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`imap-smtp-email` 技能目前安装在 **系统目录** 下，路径是：\n\n```\n/app/skills/imap-smtp-email/\n```\n\n这个目录是 OpenClaw 框架的**内置技能库**，所有预装技能都放在这里。\n\n### 📂 技能目录结构对比：\n\n| 目录类型 | 路径 | 用途 | 是否可修改 |\n|---------|------|------|-----------|\n| **系统技能** | `/app/skills/` | 预装技能（如 `imap-smtp-email`、`humanizer`） | ❌ 不建议直接修改（系统升级会覆盖） |\n| **用户技能** | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` | 你自己写或下载的技能 | ✅ 完全自由修改、添加、删除 |\n\n### 🔍 如何查看这个技能的内容？\n你可以用 `read` 命令查看它的核心文件，比如：\n```bash\nread /app/skills/imap-smtp-email/SKILL.md\n```\n或者查看配置脚本：\n```bash\nread /app/skills/imap-smtp-email/setup.sh\n```\n\n### 💡 如果你想“备份”或“自定义”这个技能：\n1. **复制一份到用户目录**：\n   ```bash\n   cp -r /app/skills/imap-smtp-email ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n   ```\n2. **在用户目录修改**：\n   修改 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email/SKILL.md` 或其他文件，不会影响系统原版。\n3. **优先加载用户版**：\n   如果两个目录都有同名技能，OpenClaw 会优先用 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` 里的版本！\n\n需要我帮你看看这个技能的具体实现，或者帮你复制一份到用户目录吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":22878,"output":410,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23288,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776173647365,"responseId":"chatcmpl-381f5653-af5e-47db-a970-1056d9419f97"}}
