{"type":"message","id":"bdfff86e","parentId":"88bbc7f7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:35:37.040Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`/app/skills/` 目录下目前只有 **3 个系统内置技能**：\n\n1. **`apple-notes`** 🍎 - 处理 Apple Notes 相关功能\n2. **`humanizer`** 🧹 - 去除 AI 写作痕迹，让文字更自然\n3. **`security-triage`** 🛡️ - GitHub 安全公告快速评估\n\n**注意**：`imap-smtp-email` **不在**这个系统目录下！它只存在于你的用户目录 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` 中（刚才查过了）。\n\n这说明：\n- 系统原版没有预装 `imap-smtp-email`。\n- 它是**用户手动安装/复制**到你工作空间的（可能是你之前装过，或者从社区下载的）。\n- 你可以自由修改它，不用担心系统升级覆盖。\n\n需要我帮你看看 `imap-smtp-email` 在用户目录下的具体文件，或者检查一下它的配置状态吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":23912,"output":214,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24126,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776173733264,"responseId":"chatcmpl-df38d2a6-5e1a-4e2a-89e4-476eaa384568"}}
