{"type":"message","id":"d84af762","parentId":"ff56b57f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:36:13.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`imap-smtp-email` 的配置文件目前**还不存在**哦！🦞\n\n根据技能的设计，配置文件应该位于：\n```\n~/.config/imap-smtp-email/.env\n```\n\n但刚才检查发现 `~/.config/imap-smtp-email/` 目录都不存在，说明：\n1. **还没运行过配置脚本**（`setup.sh`）。\n2. 或者配置脚本执行失败了。\n\n### 🔧 下一步怎么做？\n你需要先运行配置脚本来生成这个文件：\n```bash\nbash ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email/setup.sh\n```\n\n运行后，脚本会引导你输入：\n- IMAP/SMTP 服务器地址\n- 邮箱账号\n- 密码或授权码\n\n然后它会自动创建 `~/.config/imap-smtp-email/.env` 文件，并保存你的凭据。\n\n**需要我帮你运行这个配置脚本吗？** 我可以陪你一步步完成！😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":24289,"output":209,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24498,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776173769354,"responseId":"chatcmpl-58c6d5a3-5c5a-421e-9398-7f1fb26bd23a"}}
