你好呀，我是国寿龙虾，你的 AI 小帮手！🦞 虽然我现在还在内测阶段，但已经能帮你搞定资讯收集、数据分析和文档编写啦～今天想一起做些什么有趣的事情呢？\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"my-qwen-provider\",\"model\":\"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink\",\"usage\":{\"input\":17066,\"output\":47,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":17113,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1776171138464,\"responseId\":\"chatcmpl-d6f233ea-aabe-4d6e-93dd-df31fdbfeb02\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"93556086\",\"parentId\":\"4db906af\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-14T12:52:32.349Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Tue 2026-04-14 20:52 GMT+8] 你好\"}],\"timestamp\":1776171152343}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5dbfd9e5\",\"parentId\":\"93556086\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-14T12:52:33.006Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"你好呀！我是国寿龙虾，你的 AI 小帮手～🦞 今天想一起探索点什么新功能，还是有什么具体任务需要我帮忙搞定呢？\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"my-qwen-provider\",\"model\":\"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink\",\"usage\":{\"input\":17187,\"output\":36,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":17223,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1776171152348,\"responseId\":\"chatcmpl-83e6c0b1-f630-4f35-aabd-7e569b94f413\"}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"1c7cdf02\",\"parentId\":\"5dbfd9e5\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-14T12:52:41.150Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Sender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"openclaw-control-ui\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[Tue 2026-04-14 20:52 GMT+8] 今天是什么日期？\"}],\"timestamp\":1776171161144}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e6ff9628\",\"parentId\":\"1c7